Name: Dungeon Escape
About the game: Challenging 2D platformer with simple graphics and great chiptune soundtrack. Try to get out of a dangerous dungeon full of enemies and traps. Features: Minimalistic graphics Hardcore gameplay Great original Soundtrack Many levels Enemies blast if jump on their heads Coins! Who does not like a coins? Can you pass all the tests and get out of a dangerous dungeon?
